{"tid":2516702,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"［非正式統計］想收集在倫人士嘅使費","createTime":"2021-05-04T23:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T23:08:05.000Z","uid":188643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca3790ff15db1c0a9797717d912d34932f62e91","tid":2516702,"uid":188643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T23:08:05.000Z","msg":"倫敦巴絲打有無興趣分享一下月使費？<br />\n<br />\n出發前感恩有前人嘅分享，因為參考咗好幾個唔同個案，亦都因為官網有完整嘅數據所以有個約數可以點準備好盤數<br />\n<br />\n依家咁多位巴絲打落腳咗好一段時間，想再參考一下唔同個案嘅每月支出，想睇吓預期同現實可以有幾大出入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要想睇倫敦嘅個案<br />\n以下係一啲正式嘅統計<br />\n<br />\n2.4ppl // &pound;587.9 pw (&pound;2,548.0 pcm) // FY2020<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nimblefins.co.uk/average-uk-household-budget#nogo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nimblefins.co.uk%2Faverage-uk-household-budget%23nogo&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=0885f1b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nimblefins.co.uk/average-uk-household-budget#nogo</a><br />\n<br />\n2.4ppl // &pound;592.0 pw // FY2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ons.gov.uk/peoplepopulationandcommunity/personalandhouseholdfinances/expenditure/bulletins/familyspendingintheuk/april2018tomarch2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ons.gov.uk%2Fpeoplepopulationandcommunity%2Fpersonalandhouseholdfinances%2Fexpenditure%2Fbulletins%2Ffamilyspendingintheuk%2Fapril2018tomarch2019&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK1m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=c1fd9eda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ons.gov.uk/peoplepopulationandcommunity/personalandhouseholdfinances/expenditure/bulletins/familyspendingintheuk/april2018tomarch2019</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝分享嘅各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}